      <title>Lyft 的山火救援工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/lyft-s-wildfire-relief-efforts-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着洛杉矶山火持续肆虐，Lyft 首席政策官 Jerry Golden 概述了该公司如何努力帮助撤离人员。他与 Caroline Hyde 一起在“彭博科技”节目中讨论这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/lyft-s-wildfire-relief-efforts-video</guid>
